channel.title: Strictly Come Dancing
channel.desc: The frights keep coming on Strictly's Halloween weekend as our couples find out the results. Our professionals invite you along to a monsters' ball, and there's music from Cat Burns. As the witching hour approaches, two more couples will be sent down into the dreaded dance-off, and for one of them, the die is cast. Who will be banished from the ballroom for good?
